 Hold Steady的Craig Finn分享了“物质人物”，并宣布新专辑“总是”，以Sam Fender，The Drugs和Kathleen Edwards为主题https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-hold-steadys-craig-finn-shares-people-people-ople-ople-fin-substance-and-announces-new-new-album-album-always-bum-always-always-featuring-sam-fender-在停药和凯瑟琳 -  3833850？是在击球手和凯瑟琳 - 卫队的击球手Max PilleySun, 02 Feb 2025 22:30:34 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3833850 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>毒品战争的亚当·格兰迪尔（Adam Granduciel）制作了该唱片，该记录在四月</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-hold-steadys-craig-finn-shares-people-of-substance-and-announces-new-album-always-been-featuring-sam-fender-the-war-on-drugs-and-kathleen-edwards-3833850">Hold Stestent的Craig Finn的帖子分享了“物质人物”，并宣布以Sam Fender为主题的新专辑，毒品战争和凯瑟琳·爱德华兹（Kathleen Edwards）</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/craig_finn_hold-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-hold-steady">Hold Steady的</a>主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/craig-finn">克雷格·芬恩（Craig Finn）</a>宣布了他的新个人专辑“ Beyways”，并分享了单曲“物质的人”  - 在下面听。</p><p>这将是歌手的第六张个人专辑，将于4月4日通过Tamarac Records/Thirty Tigers发行。您可以<a href="https://orcd.co/cf-ab" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订/预添加您的副本。</p><p> “物质人士”现在正在流媒体服务中，并看到Finn带回了他的商标Droll Flyrical风格，以丰富的美洲风味全乐队的支持。听曲目并在此处观看视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="克雷格·芬恩（Craig Finn） - 实质的人" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ckhsMBuUWIM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>克雷格·芬恩（Craig Finn）说：“我认为这是我创造的最叙述记录。” “大多数歌曲都涉及一个主人公，尽管缺乏信心，他还是从事神职人员的职业。该唱片讲述了他的兴衰，堕落和救赎的故事，同时还填补了他的旅行和他所生活的世界的细节。我为我们的创造感到自豪，希望您喜欢。”</p><p>这张专辑是由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-war-on-drugs">毒品战争</a>的亚当·格兰迪尔（Adam Granduciel）在他位于加利福尼亚伯班克（Burbank）的工作室制作的，并提供了Granduciel的音乐贡献，以及凯瑟琳·爱德华兹（Kathleen Edwards）和萨姆·芬德（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender）</a>的毒品和嘉宾人声的其他成员。 </p><figure id="attachment_3833851" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833851" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833851" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Craig_Finn_Always_Been_COVER-1-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Craig_Finn_Always_Been_COVER-1-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Craig_Finn_Always_Been_COVER-1-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https: