w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gwenno_green_man-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwenno">Gwenno</a>将于本月晚些时候在伦敦举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/green-man">2025年Green Man Festival</a>举行的启动活动。</p><p>绿人是威尔士最大的独立音乐，科学和艺术节，将于8月14日至17日在Brecon信标的Glanusk Estate网站上庆祝其23年。阵容尚未宣布。</p><p>现在，音乐节的组织者宣布了2月28日在伦敦列克星敦举行的2025年阵容的启动活动。现场音乐的夜晚将展出Gwenno，Bob Dylan Tribute Act Broadside Hacks和伦敦二人组合银色的血腥，其次是深夜DJ。</p><p>活动还将在活动中进行抽奖活动，为与会者提供了赢得2025年Green Man 2025的两张门票的机会。发射活动的门票可<a href="https://dice.fm/partner/green-man/event/yol3gv-green-man-line-up-launch-party-28th-feb-the-lexington-london-tickets?dice_campaign=Green+Man&amp;dice_channel=web&amp;dice_feature=mio_marketing&amp;dice_id=5079374&amp;dice_tags=organic" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>获得。 </p><figure id="attachment_3833838" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833838" style="width: 1200px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833838" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Green-Man-The-Lexington-Launch-Line-up-poster-1.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="1200" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Green-Man-The-Lexington-Launch-Line-up-poster-1.jpg 1200w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Green-Man-The-Lexington-Launch-Line-up-poster-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Green-Man-The-Lexington-Launch-Line-up-poster-1-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Green-Man-The-Lexington-Launch-Line-up-poster-1-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Green-Man-The-Lexington-Launch-Line-up-poster-1-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Green-Man-The-Lexington-Launch-Line-up-poster-1-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833838" class="wp-caption-text">绿人发射秀海报。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>格温诺（Gwenno）最近是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gwenno-and-redolent-announced-as-independent-venue-week-2025-ambassadors-3817928">2025年独立地点周的大使之一</a>，该周日（2月2日）结束。歌手兼作曲家和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>提名人是威尔士的代表，并于1月29日（1月29日）在加的夫的阿卡佩拉工作室（Cardiff&#39;s Acapela Studio）演出。</p><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-pipettes">移液器</a>歌手发行了三张个人专辑，最近一次是2022年的“ Tresor”，该专辑几乎完全以康沃尔为特色。</p><p>去年的《绿人节》（Green Man Festival）是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/big-thief">Big Thief</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sampha">Sampha</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleaford-mods">Sleaford Mods</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jon-hopkins">Jon Hopkins</a>的头条新闻， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jesus-and-the-mary-chain">The Jesus and Mary Chain</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-country-new-road">Black Country，New Road</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondshell">Blondshell</a>又出现了其他露面。</p><p>它还看到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-big-moons-juliette-jackson-marries-partner-at-green-man-festival-10-years-after-they-met-on-the-same-site-3784676">大月亮的朱丽叶·杰克逊（Juliette Jackson）与她的搭档麦克斯（Max）结婚</a>，这是他们第一次在音乐节上相遇10年，而他们俩都为秘密邮局（Secret Post Office）提供包裹，这项免费服务允许节日活动者发送信件和卡片。给现场的其他人。马克斯还在2019年在绿人队的乐队演出期间向歌手求婚。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gwenno-bob-dylan-tribute-and-more-for-green-man-2025-london-launch-event-3833837">Gwenno邮政，Bob Dylan致敬和Green Man 2025伦敦发射赛的更多活动</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
